        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[State Sales and Income Tax Deduction Fairness Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow: (1) the State and local income tax deduction against the alternative minimum tax; and (2) the deduction of State and local general sales taxes in lieu of State and local income taxes.]]></text>
      </summary>
